<lb ed="I" n="0151a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>郭猛八十人等造塔像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0151a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0151a0101">　□□天保八年歲次丁丑三月
<lb ed="I" n="0151a02" type="honorific"/>　庚子廿二日<note n="0151001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30506"/>＝辛【史】</note><app n="0151001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30506"/></rdg></app>酉。法儀兄弟八
<lb ed="I" n="0151a03" type="honorific"/>　十人等。故仰囑慈雲。希心洪澤。
<lb ed="I" n="0151a04" type="honorific"/>　府練財命。知有浮<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">死</unclear>之速。藉今
<lb ed="I" n="0151a05" type="honorific"/>　現在。各減家珍。詳建妙塔一軀。
<lb ed="I" n="0151a06" type="honorific"/>　上為皇永隆。<note n="0151002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30877"/>＝邊【史】</note><app n="0151002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30877"/></rdg></app>方寧太。又願居
<lb ed="I" n="0151a07" type="honorific"/>　眷三有之徒。咸同此福。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">法</unclear>仙
<lb ed="I" n="0151a08" type="honorific"/>　寶　高樹　淳于思孫道慈
<lb ed="I" n="0151a09" type="honorific"/>郭良生牟仙　陳寶　趙羅剎
<lb ed="I" n="0151a10" type="honorific"/>侯眾　牟光　淳于國　孔神
<lb ed="I" n="0151a11" type="honorific"/>　□洛生牟見祖淳于興劉賓陰始
<lb ed="I" n="0151a12" type="honorific"/>　□<note n="0151003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30878"/>＝那【史】</note><app n="0151003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30878"/></rdg></app>陰思達孔詳夏侯珇淳于猛
<lb ed="I" n="0151a13" type="honorific"/>　□<app type="star" corresp="#0151003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30878"/></rdg></app>牟<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">豊</unclear>　牟本　孫万年王市
<lb ed="I" n="0151a14" type="honorific"/>　□<app type="star" corresp="#0151003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30878"/></rdg></app>孔王子王祖興劉葙　孔景
<lb ed="I" n="0151a15" type="honorific"/>維<app type="star" corresp="#0151003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30878"/></rdg></app>陰由　<g ref="#CB30876"/>元伯丁族　陰小
<lb ed="I" n="0151a16" type="honorific"/>維<app type="star" corresp="#0151003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">那</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30878"/></rdg></app>牟<note n="0151004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤋜＝照【史】</note><app n="0151004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤋜</rdg></app>明牟<note n="0151005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30879"/>＝袁【史】</note><app n="0151005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">袁</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30879"/></rdg></app>　王秋孫曇<note n="0151006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31161"/>＝度【史】</note><app n="0151006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">度</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31161"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0151a17" type="honorific"/>劉<note n="0151007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨕞＝遷【史】</note><app n="0151007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨕞</rdg></app>刑道元張景達孔惠可
<lb ed="I" n="0151a18" type="honorific"/>淳于周淳于<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">躭</unclear>矯念
<lb ed="I" n="0151a19" type="honorific"/>牟槙興逢懟牟視犢牟仙供養
<lb ed="I" n="0151a20" type="honorific"/>陰□牟寄興陰□牟苗孔平
<lb ed="I" n="0151a21" type="honorific"/>天保八年
<lb ed="I" n="0151a22" type="honorific"/>郭
<lb ed="I" n="0151a23" type="honorific"/>猛
<lb ed="I" n="0151a24" type="honorific"/>造
<lb ed="I" n="0151a25" type="honorific"/>像
<lb ed="I" n="0151a26" type="honorific"/>一摳
<lb ed="I" n="0151a27" type="honorific"/>□崇伯陰永陰樹陰路牟六
<lb ed="I" n="0151a28" type="honorific"/>陰叉陰景洪孔王子供養時
<lb ed="I" n="0151a29" type="honorific"/>鄧<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">戀</unclear>矢岑陵王張<app type="star" corresp="#0151004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤋜</rdg></app>堂
<lb ed="I" n="0151a30" type="honorific"/>劉勝王王銀珠張妍陰神
<lb ed="I" n="0151a31" type="honorific"/>洛仙姜王閏妃逢妙孔女伾
<lb ed="I" n="0151a32" type="honorific"/>陰子洪牟信陰愁羊蒲堂
<lb ed="I" n="0151a33" type="honorific"/>　　塔主牟光
<lb ed="I" n="0151a34" type="honorific"/>英〃妙塔。內置聖容。流光綴
<lb ed="I" n="0151a35" type="honorific"/>彩。影<note n="0151008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥆮＝眺【史】</note><app n="0151008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">眺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥆮</rdg></app>三空。
<lb ed="I" n="0151a36" type="honorific"/>顒〃哲士。敬法詵〃。悁財非
<lb ed="I" n="0151a37" type="honorific"/>寶。崇福為珍。
<lb ed="I" n="0151a38" type="honorific"/>施石人劉永固</p>
